510426,113,2312,121,130,1,23,5,‘‘ Tena hi evaṃ karothā’’ ti. 
510427,113,2312,131,143,1,74,10,Tadā bodhisatto takkāriyo nāma māṇavo hutvā tassa santike sippaṃ uggaṇhāti. 
