511006,113,2585,50,77,1,178,20,"So attano baddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ idāneva baddharavaṃ ravissāmi, ñātakāme bhayatajjitā gocaraṃ aggahetvāva palāyissanti, yāva etesaṃ gocaraggahaṇaṃ, tāva adhivāsessāmī’’ ti. "
