511261,113,2749,77,87,1,27,6,‘‘ atthi pana te koci mitto’’ ti?
511262,113,2749,88,95,1,16,3,‘‘ Natthi bhadde’’ ti. 
511263,113,2749,96,113,1,111,16,"Amhākaṃ uppannaṃ bhayaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā haraṇasamatthaṃ mittaṃ vā sahāyaṃ vā laddhuṃ vaṭṭati, mitte tāva gaṇhāhīti."
511264,113,2749,114,124,1,36,6,‘‘ Kehi saddhiṃ mettiṃ karomi bhadde’’ ti? 
511265,113,2749,125,137,1,104,10,"Pācīnapasse vasantena ukkusarājena, uttarapasse sīhena, jātassaramajjhe kacchapena saddhiṃ mettiṃ karohīti. "
