511407,113,2833,24,49,1,163,19,"Athassa aguṇaṃ pakāsentā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma bhikkhu evarūpe niyyānikasāsane pabbajitvā kuhanaṃ nissāya jīvikaṃ kappetī’’ ti. "
511408,113,2833,50,90,1,160,23,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa kuhakoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
