511763,113,3022,2,7,1,19,2,[ 489]6. Surucijātakavaṇṇanā 
511764,113,3023,2,21,1,143,16,Mahesī surucino {bhariyā}ti idaṃ satthā sāvatthiṃ upanissāya migāramātupāsāde viharanto visākhāya mahāupāsikāya laddhe aṭṭha vare ārabbha kathesi. 
511765,113,3023,22,34,1,109,12,Sā hi ekadivasaṃ jetavane dhammakathaṃ sutvā bhagavantaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena svātanāya nimantetvā pakkāmi. 
511766,113,3023,35,43,1,57,7,Tassā pana rattiyā accayena cātuddīpiko mahāmegho pāvassi . 
511767,113,3023,44,84,1,257,29,"Bhagavā bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ yathā, bhikkhave, jetavane vassati, evaṃ catūsu dīpesu vassati, ovassāpetha, bhikkhave, kāyaṃ, ayaṃ pacchimako cātuddīpiko mahāmegho’’ ti vatvā ovassāpitakāyehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ iddhibalena jetavane antarahito visākhāya koṭṭhake pāturahosi. "
511768,113,3023,85,142,1,377,44,"Upāsikā‘‘ acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, tathāgatassa mahiddhikatā mahānubhāvatā, yatra hi nāma jāṇukamattesupi oghesu vattamānesu kaṭimattesupi oghesu vattamānesu na hi nāma ekabhikkhussapi pādā vā cīvarāni vā allāni bhavissantī’’ ti haṭṭhā udaggā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ parivisitvā katabhattakiccaṃ bhagavantaṃ etadavoca‘‘ aṭṭhāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ varāni yācāmī’’ ti."
511769,113,3023,143,154,1,38,5,"‘‘ Atikkantavarā kho, visākhe, tathāgatā’’ ti."
511770,113,3023,155,169,1,46,8,"‘‘ Yāni ca, bhante, kappiyāni yāni ca anavajjānī’’ ti."
511771,113,3023,170,177,1,17,3,‘‘ Vadehi visākhe’’ ti.
511772,113,3023,178,214,1,245,23,"‘‘ Icchāmahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhusaṅghassa yāvajīvaṃ vassikasāṭikaṃ dātuṃ, āgantukabhattaṃ dātuṃ, gamikabhattaṃ dātuṃ, gilānabhattaṃ dātuṃ, gilānupaṭṭhākabhattaṃ dātuṃ, gilānabhesajjaṃ dātuṃ, dhuvayāguṃ dātuṃ, bhikkhunisaṅghassa yāvajīvaṃ udakasāṭikaṃ dātun’’ ti. "
511773,113,3024,2,66,1,311,44,"Satthā ‘‘ kaṃ pana tvaṃ, visākhe, atthavasaṃ sampassamānā tathāgataṃ aṭṭha varāni yācasī’’ ti pucchitvā tāya varānisaṃse kathite‘‘ sādhu sādhu, visākhe, sādhu kho tvaṃ, visākhe, imaṃ ānisaṃsaṃ sampassamānā tathāgataṃ aṭṭha varāni yācasī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ anujānāmi te, visākhe, aṭṭha varānī’’ ti aṭṭha vare datvā anumodanaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
511774,113,3024,67,94,1,191,21,"Athekadivasaṃ satthari pubbārāme viharante bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, visākhā mahāupāsikā mātugāmattabhāve ṭhatvāpi dasabalassa santike aṭṭha vare labhi, aho mahāguṇā’’ ti. "
511775,113,3024,95,141,1,193,28,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, visākhā idāneva mama santikā vare labhati, pubbepesā labhiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
511776,113,3025,2,21,1,105,14,Atīte mithilāyaṃ suruci nāma rājā rajjaṃ kārento puttaṃ paṭilabhitvā tassa‘‘ surucikumāro’’ tveva nāmaṃ akāsi. 
511777,113,3025,22,36,1,83,10,So vayappatto‘‘ takkasilāyaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhissāmī’’ ti gantvā nagaradvāre sālāyaṃ nisīdi. 
511778,113,3025,37,47,1,101,9,Bārāṇasiraññopi putto brahmadattakumāro nāma tatheva gantvā surucikumārassa nisinnaphalakeyeva nisīdi. 
511779,113,3025,48,99,1,359,43,"Te aññamaññaṃ pucchitvā vissāsikā hutvā ekatova ācariyassa santikaṃ gantvā ācariyabhāgaṃ datvā sippaṃ paṭṭhapetvā na cirasseva niṭṭhitasippā ācariyaṃ āpucchitvā thokaṃ maggaṃ ekatova gantvā dvedhāpathe ṭhitā aññamaññaṃ āliṅgitvā mittadhammānurakkhaṇatthaṃ katikaṃ kariṃsu‘‘ sace mama putto jāyati, tava dhītā, tava putto, mama dhītā, tesaṃ āvāhavivāhaṃ karissāmā’’ ti. "
511780,113,3025,100,115,1,86,10,"Tesu rajjaṃ kārentesu surucimahārājassa putto jāyi,‘‘ surucikumāro’’ tvevassa nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
