511782,113,3026,2,9,1,69,7,Surucikumāro vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ gantvā sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā āgacchi. 
511783,113,3026,10,38,1,171,23,"Atha naṃ pitā rajje abhisiñcitukāmo hutvā‘‘ sahāyassa kira me bārāṇasirañño dhītā atthi, tamevassa aggamahesiṃ karissāmī’’ ti tassā atthāya bahuṃ paṇṇākāraṃ datvā amacce pesesi. "
