512120,113,3195,2,7,1,21,2,[ 491]8. Mahāmorajātakavaṇṇanā 
512121,113,3196,2,17,1,104,13,Sace hi tyāhaṃ dhanahetu {gāhito}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
512122,113,3196,18,72,1,313,38,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu ayaṃ nandīrāgo tādisaṃ kiṃ nāma nālolessati, na hi sineruubbāhanakavāto sāmante purāṇapaṇṇassa lajjati, pubbe satta vassasatāni antokilesasamudācāraṃ vāretvā viharante visuddhasattepesa ālolesiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
