512124,113,3197,15,22,1,61,7,Gabbhe paripākagate mātā gocarabhūmiyaṃ aṇḍaṃ pātetvā pakkāmi. 
512125,113,3197,23,34,1,91,11,Aṇḍañca nāma mātu arogabhāve sati aññasmiṃ dīghajātikādiparipanthe ca avijjamāne na nassati. 
512126,113,3197,35,50,1,127,14,"Tasmā taṃ aṇḍaṃ kaṇikāramakulaṃ viya suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ hutvā pariṇatakāle attano dhammatāya bhijji, suvaṇṇavaṇṇo moracchāpo nikkhami. "
512127,113,3197,51,65,1,120,12,"Tassa dve akkhīni jiñjukāphalasadisāni, tuṇḍaṃ pavāḷavaṇṇaṃ, tisso rattarājiyo gīvaṃ parikkhipitvā piṭṭhimajjhena agamaṃsu. "
512128,113,3197,66,71,1,52,5,So vayappatto bhaṇḍasakaṭamattasarīro abhirūpo ahosi. 
512129,113,3197,72,79,1,59,7,Taṃ sabbe nīlamorā sannipatitvā rājānaṃ katvā parivārayiṃsu. 
512130,113,3198,2,35,1,237,26,"So ekadivasaṃ udakasoṇḍiyaṃ pānīyaṃ pivanto attano rūpasampattiṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ ahaṃ sabbamorehi atirekarūpasobho, sacāhaṃ imehi saddhiṃ manussapathe vasissāmi, paripantho me uppajjissati, himavantaṃ gantvā ekakova phāsukaṭṭhāne vasissāmī’’ ti. "
512131,113,3198,36,68,1,272,30,"So rattibhāge moresu paṭisallīnesu kañci ajānāpetvā uppatitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā tisso pabbatarājiyo atikkamma catutthāya pabbatarājiyā ekasmiṃ araññe padumasañchanno jātassaro atthi, tassa avidūre ekaṃ pabbataṃ nissāya ṭhito mahānigrodharukkho atthi, tassa sākhāya nilīyi. "
512132,113,3198,69,76,1,48,7,Tassa pana pabbatassa vemajjhe manāpā guhā atthi. 
512133,113,3198,77,85,1,59,8,So tattha vasitukāmo hutvā tassā pamukhe pabbatatale nilīyi. 
512134,113,3198,86,102,1,118,12,"Taṃ pana ṭhānaṃ neva heṭṭhābhāgena abhiruhituṃ, na uparibhāgena otarituṃ sakkā, biḷāladīghajātikamanussabhayehi vimuttaṃ. "
512135,113,3198,103,163,1,454,48,So‘‘ idaṃ me phāsukaṭṭhānan’’ ti taṃ divasaṃ tattheva vasitvā punadivase pabbataguhāto uṭṭhāya pabbatamatthake puratthābhimukho nisinno udentaṃ sūriyamaṇḍalaṃ disvā attano divārakkhāvaraṇatthāya‘‘ udetayaṃ cakkhumā ekarājā’’ ti parittaṃ katvā gocarabhūmiyaṃ otaritvā gocaraṃ gahetvā sāyaṃ āgantvā pabbatamatthake pacchābhimukho nisinno atthaṅgataṃ sūriyamaṇḍalaṃ disvā attano rattirakkhāvaraṇatthāya‘‘ apetayaṃ cakkhumā ekarājā’’ ti parittaṃ katvā etenupāyena vasati. 
512136,113,3199,2,19,1,140,17,Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ eko luddaputto araññe vicaranto pabbatamatthake nisinnaṃ moraṃ disvā attano nivesanaṃ āgantvā maraṇāsannakāle puttaṃ āha–
512137,113,3199,20,39,1,95,12,"‘‘ tāta, catutthāya pabbatarājiyā araññe suvaṇṇavaṇṇo moro atthi, sace rājā pucchati, ācikkheyyāsī’’ ti. "
512138,113,3199,40,49,1,79,9,Athekasmiṃ divase bārāṇasirañño khemā nāma aggamahesī paccūsakāle supinaṃ passi. 
512139,113,3199,50,53,1,20,3,Evarūpo supino ahosi–
512140,113,3199,54,74,1,104,14,"‘‘ suvaṇṇavaṇṇo moro dhammaṃ deseti, sā sādhukāraṃ datvā dhammaṃ suṇāti, moro dhammaṃ desetvā uṭṭhāya pakkāmi’’. "
512141,113,3199,75,119,1,205,30,"Sā‘‘ morarājā gacchati, gaṇhatha nan’’ ti vadantīyeva pabujjhi, pabujjhitvā ca pana supinabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ supinoti vutte rājā na ādaraṃ karissati,‘ dohaḷo me’ ti vutte karissatī’’ ti cintetvā dohaḷinī viya hutvā nipajji. "
512142,113,3199,120,135,1,61,10,"Atha naṃ rājā upasaṅkamitvā pucchi‘‘ bhadde, kiṃ te aphāsukan’’ ti."
512143,113,3199,136,144,1,20,4,‘‘ Dohaḷo me uppanno’’ ti.
512144,113,3199,145,153,1,21,4,‘‘ Kiṃ icchasi bhadde’’ ti?
512145,113,3199,154,164,1,45,6,‘‘ Suvaṇṇavaṇṇassa morassa dhammaṃ sotuṃ devā’’ ti.
512146,113,3199,165,176,1,38,6,"‘‘ Bhadde, kuto evarūpaṃ moraṃ lacchāmī’’ ti?"
512147,113,3199,177,191,1,41,8,"‘‘ Deva, sace na labhāmi, jīvitaṃ me natthī’’ ti."
512148,113,3199,192,233,1,192,27,"‘‘ Bhadde, mā cintayi, sace katthaci atthi, labhissasī’’ ti rājā naṃ assāsetvā gantvā rājāsane nisinno amacce pucchi‘‘ ambho, devī suvaṇṇavaṇṇassa morassa dhammaṃ sotukāmā, morā nāma suvaṇṇavaṇṇā hontī’’ ti?"
512149,113,3199,234,242,1,27,4,‘‘ Brāhmaṇā jānissanti devā’’ ti. 
512150,113,3200,2,6,1,33,4,Rājā brāhmaṇe pakkosāpetvā pucchi. 
512151,113,3200,7,33,1,183,21,"Brāhmaṇā evamāhaṃsu‘‘ mahārāja jalajesu macchakacchapakakkaṭakā, thalajesu migā haṃsā morā tittirā ete tiracchānagatā ca manussā ca suvaṇṇavaṇṇā hontīti amhākaṃ lakkhaṇamantesu āgatan’’ ti. "
512152,113,3200,34,49,1,85,11,Rājā attano vijite luddaputte sannipātetvā‘‘ suvaṇṇavaṇṇo moro vo diṭṭhapubbo’’ ti pucchi. 
512153,113,3200,50,60,1,29,5,Sesā‘‘ na diṭṭhapubbo’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
