512156,113,3200,91,116,1,122,19,"Atha naṃ rājā‘‘ samma, mayhañca deviyā ca jīvitaṃ dinnaṃ bhavissati, gantvā taṃ bandhitvā ānehī’’ ti bahuṃ dhanaṃ datvā uyyojesi. "
512157,113,3200,117,144,1,159,21,"So puttadārassa dhanaṃ datvā tattha gantvā mahāsattaṃ disvā pāse oḍḍetvā‘‘ ajja bajjhissati, ajja bajjhissatī’’ ti abajjhitvāva mato, devīpi patthanaṃ alabhantī matā. "
512158,113,3200,145,185,1,246,31,"Rājā‘‘ taṃ moraṃ nissāya piyabhariyā me matā’’ ti kujjhitvā kodhavasiko hutvā‘‘ himavante catutthāya pabbatarājiyā suvaṇṇavaṇṇo moro carati, tassa maṃsaṃ khāditvā ajarā amarā hontī’’ ti suvaṇṇapaṭṭe likhāpetvā taṃ paṭṭaṃ sāramañjūsāyaṃ ṭhapetvā kālamakāsi. "
