512168,113,3202,2,62,1,378,49,"Atha naṃ luddaputto yaṭṭhiagge olambantaṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ imaṃ morarājaṃ cha luddaputtā bandhituṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, ahampi satta vassāni nāsakkhiṃ, ajja panesa imaṃ moriṃ nissāya kilesāturo hutvā parittaṃ kātuṃ asakkuṇitvā āgamma pāse baddho heṭṭhāsīsako olambati, evarūpo me sīlavā kilamito, evarūpaṃ rañño paṇṇākāratthāya netuṃ ayuttaṃ, kiṃ me raññā dinnena sakkārena, vissajjessāmi nan’’ ti. "
