513002,113,3718,23,42,1,108,14,"Thero‘ nāyaṃ mayhaṃ anucchaviko’ ti dhammasenāpatino adāsi, sopi‘ nāyaṃ mayhaṃ anucchaviko’ ti tathāgatassa adāsi. "
513003,113,3718,43,71,1,206,22,"Tathāgato aññaṃ uttaritaraṃ apassanto attano dhammassāmitāya‘ mayhameveso anucchaviko’ ti taṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paribhuñji, cīvarasāṭakepi gaṇhi, evaṃ so piṇḍapāto yathānucchavikatāya dhammassāminova pādamūlaṃ gato’’ ti. "
