513374,113,3908,145,153,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, mayā’’ ti."
513375,113,3908,154,201,1,236,33,"‘‘ Nassa, vasala, caṇḍāla kāḷakaṇṇi mā idha vasi, heṭṭhāsote vasāhī’’ ti vatvā heṭṭhāsote vasantenapi tena pātite dantakaṭṭhe paṭisotaṃ āgantvā jaṭāsu laggante so‘‘ nassa vasala, sace idha vasissasi, sattame divase sattadhā muddhā phalissatī’’ ti āha. "
513376,113,3909,2,24,1,140,16,"Mahāsatto ‘‘ sacāhaṃ etassa kujjhissāmi, sīlaṃ me arakkhitaṃ bhavissati, upāyenevassa mānaṃ bhindissāmī’’ ti sattame divase sūriyuggamanaṃ nivāresi. "
513377,113,3909,25,42,1,98,12,"Manussā ubbāḷhā jātimantaṃ tāpasaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, tumhe sūriyuggamanaṃ na dethā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
513378,113,3909,43,45,1,6,2,So āha–
513379,113,3909,46,64,1,77,12,"‘‘ na me taṃ kammaṃ, nadītīre paneko caṇḍālo vasati, tassetaṃ kammaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. "
513380,113,3909,65,82,1,82,10,"Manussā mahāsattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ tumhe, bhante, sūriyuggamanaṃ na dethā’’ ti pucchiṃsu."
513381,113,3909,83,89,1,10,2,‘‘ Āmāvuso’’ ti.
513382,113,3909,90,96,1,12,2,‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti.
513383,113,3909,97,117,1,125,15,"‘‘ Tumhākaṃ kulūpako tāpaso maṃ niraparādhaṃ abhisapi, tasmiṃ āgantvā khamāpanatthāya mama pādesu patite sūriyaṃ vissajjessāmī’’ ti. "
513384,113,3909,118,136,1,113,14,Te gantvā taṃ kaḍḍhantā ānetvā mahāsattassa pādamūle nipajjāpetvā khamāpetvā āhaṃsu‘‘ sūriyaṃ vissajjetha bhante’’ ti.
513385,113,3909,137,153,1,79,10,"‘‘ Na sakkā vissajjetuṃ, sacāhaṃ vissajjessāmi, imassa sattadhā muddhā phalissatī’’ ti."
513386,113,3909,154,165,1,25,5,"‘‘ Atha, bhante, kiṃ karomā’’ ti? "
513387,113,3909,166,191,1,133,17,So‘‘ mattikāpiṇḍaṃ āharathā’’ ti āharāpetvā‘‘ imaṃ tāpasassa sīse ṭhapetvā tāpasaṃ otāretvā udake ṭhapethā’’ ti ṭhapāpetvā sūriyaṃ vissajjesi. 
513388,113,3909,192,201,1,75,8,"Sūriyarasmīhi pahaṭamatte mattikāpiṇḍo sattadhā bhijji, tāpaso udake nimujji. "
513389,113,3910,2,42,1,203,28,Mahāsatto taṃ dametvā‘‘ kahaṃ nu kho dāni soḷasa brāhmaṇasahassāni vasantī’’ ti upadhārento‘‘ majjharañño santike’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ te damessāmī’’ ti iddhiyā gantvā nagarasāmante otaritvā pattaṃ ādāya nagare piṇḍāya cari. 
513390,113,3910,43,79,1,174,26,"Brāhmaṇā taṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ idha ekaṃ dve divase vasantopi amhe appatiṭṭhe karissatī’’ ti vegena gantvā‘‘ mahārāja, māyākāro eko vijjādharo coro āgato, gaṇhāpetha nan’’ ti rañño ārocesuṃ. "
513391,113,3910,80,88,1,25,4,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
513392,113,3910,89,98,1,84,9,Mahāsattopi missakabhattaṃ ādāya aññataraṃ kuṭṭaṃ nissāya pīṭhikāya nisinno bhuñjati. 
513393,113,3910,99,112,1,111,12,Atha naṃ aññavihitakaṃ āhāraṃ paribhuñjamānameva raññā pahitapurisā asinā gīvaṃ paharitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpesuṃ. 
513394,113,3910,113,118,1,34,5,So kālaṃ katvā brahmaloke nibbatti. 
513395,113,3910,119,125,1,48,6,Imasmiṃ kira jātake bodhisatto koṇḍadamako ahosi. 
513396,113,3910,126,131,1,52,5,So teneva paratantiyuttabhāvena jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
513397,113,3910,132,141,1,95,9,Devatā kujjhitvā sakalameva majjharaṭṭhaṃ uṇhaṃ kukkuḷavassaṃ vassāpetvā raṭṭhaṃ araṭṭhamakaṃsu. 
513398,113,3910,142,144,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
513399,113,3911,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Upahacca manaṃ majjho, mātaṅgasmiṃ yasassine; "
513400,113,3912,2,21,1,45,6,"Sapārisajjo ucchinno, majjhāraññaṃ tadā ahū’’ ti.( jā.2.19.96); "
