513403,113,3914,2,4,1,28,2,Mātaṅgajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
513404,113,3916,2,7,1,26,2,[ 498]2. Cittasambhūtajātakavaṇṇanā 
513405,113,3917,2,19,1,145,17,Sabbaṃ narānaṃ saphalaṃ suciṇṇan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto āyasmato mahākassapassa piyasaṃvāse dve saddhivihārike bhikkhū ārabbha kathesi. 
513406,113,3917,20,39,1,142,16,"Te kira aññamaññaṃ appaṭivibhattabhogā paramavissāsikā ahesuṃ, piṇḍāya carantāpi ekatova gacchanti, ekatova āgacchanti, vinā bhavituṃ na sakkonti. "
513407,113,3917,40,46,1,63,6,Dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū tesaṃyeva vissāsaṃ vaṇṇayamānā nisīdiṃsu. 
513408,113,3917,47,96,1,263,32,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ anacchariyaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ ekasmiṃ attabhāve vissāsikattaṃ, porāṇakapaṇḍitā tīṇi cattāri bhavantarāni gacchantāpi mittabhāvaṃ na vijahiṃsuyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
513409,113,3918,2,9,1,62,7,Atīte avantiraṭṭhe ujjeniyaṃ avantimahārājā nāma rajjaṃ kāresi. 
513410,113,3918,10,15,1,38,5,Tadā ujjeniyā bahi caṇḍālagāmako ahosi. 
513411,113,3918,16,26,1,76,9,"Mahāsatto tattha nibbatti, aparopi satto tasseva mātucchāputto hutvā nibbatti. "
513412,113,3918,27,36,1,43,8,"Tesu eko citto nāma ahosi, eko sambhūto nāma. "
513413,113,3918,37,61,1,161,18,"Te ubhopi vayappattā caṇḍālavaṃsadhovanaṃ nāma sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā ekadivasaṃ‘‘ ujjenīnagaradvāre sippaṃ dassessāmā’’ ti eko uttaradvāre sippaṃ dassesi, eko pācīnadvāre. "
513414,113,3918,62,73,1,78,9,"Tasmiñca nagare dve diṭṭhamaṅgalikāyo ahesuṃ, ekā seṭṭhidhītā, ekā purohitadhītā. "
513415,113,3918,74,90,1,119,11,"Tā bahukhādanīyabhojanīyamālāgandhādīni gāhāpetvā‘‘ uyyānakīḷaṃ kīḷissāmā’’ ti ekā uttaradvārena nikkhami, ekā pācīnadvārena. "
513416,113,3918,91,125,1,160,21,Tā te caṇḍālaputte sippaṃ dassente disvā‘‘ ke ete’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ caṇḍālaputtā’’ ti sutvā‘‘ apassitabbayuttakaṃ vata passimhā’’ ti gandhodakena akkhīni dhovitvā nivattiṃsu. 
513417,113,3918,126,148,1,134,17,"Mahājano‘‘ are duṭṭhacaṇḍāla, tumhe nissāya mayaṃ amūlakāni surābhattādīni na labhimhā’’ ti te ubhopi bhātike pothetvā anayabyasanaṃ pāpesi. "
513418,113,3919,2,60,1,437,47,"Te paṭiladdhasaññā uṭṭhāya aññamaññassa santikaṃ gacchantā ekasmiṃ ṭhāne samāgantvā aññamaññassa taṃ dukkhuppattiṃ ārocetvā roditvā paridevitvā‘‘ kinti karissāmā’’ ti mantetvā‘‘ imaṃ amhākaṃ jātiṃ nissāya dukkhaṃ uppannaṃ, caṇḍālakammaṃ kātuṃ na sakkhissāma, jātiṃ paṭicchādetvā brāhmaṇamāṇavavaṇṇena takkasilaṃ gantvā sippaṃ uggaṇhissāmā’’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ katvā tattha gantvā dhammantevāsikā hutvā disāpāmokkhācariyassa santike sippaṃ paṭṭhapesuṃ. "
513419,113,3919,61,75,1,80,10,Jambudīpatale‘‘ dve kira caṇḍālā jātiṃ paṭicchādetvā sippaṃ uggaṇhantī’’ ti sūyittha. 
513420,113,3919,76,85,1,66,8,"Tesu cittapaṇḍitassa sippaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ, sambhūtassa na tāva niṭṭhāti. "
513421,113,3920,2,14,1,76,8,Athekadivasaṃ eko gāmavāsī‘‘ brāhmaṇavācanakaṃ karissāmī’’ ti ācariyaṃ nimantesi. 
513422,113,3920,15,22,1,52,7,Tameva rattiṃ devo vassitvā magge kandarādīni pūresi. 
513423,113,3920,23,52,1,173,23,"Ācariyo pātova cittapaṇḍitaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tāta, ahaṃ gantuṃ na sakkhissāmi, tvaṃ māṇavehi saddhiṃ gantā maṅgalaṃ vatvā tumhehi laddhaṃ bhuñjitvā amhehi laddhaṃ āharā’’ ti pesesi. "
513424,113,3920,53,63,1,33,6,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti māṇavake gahetvā gato. 
513425,113,3920,64,78,1,95,13,"Yāva māṇavā nhāyanti ceva mukhāni ca dhovanti, tāva manussā pāyāsaṃ vaḍḍhetvā nibbātūti ṭhapesuṃ. "
513426,113,3920,79,84,1,44,5,Māṇavā tasmiṃ anibbuteyeva āgantvā nisīdiṃsu. 
513427,113,3920,85,92,1,56,7,Manussā dakkhiṇodakaṃ datvā tesaṃ purato pātiyo ṭhapesuṃ. 
513428,113,3920,93,116,1,129,17,"Sambhūto luddhadhātuko viya hutvā‘‘ sītalo’’ ti saññāya pāyāsapiṇḍaṃ ukkhipitvā mukhe ṭhapesi, so tassa ādittaayoguḷo viya mukhaṃ dahi. "
513429,113,3920,117,134,1,94,12,So kampamāno satiṃ anupaṭṭhāpetvā cittapaṇḍitaṃ oloketvā caṇḍālabhāsāya eva‘‘ khaḷu khaḷū’’ ti āha . 
513430,113,3920,135,149,1,75,10,Sopi tatheva satiṃ anupaṭṭhāpetvā caṇḍālabhāsāya eva‘‘ niggala niggalā’’ ti āha. 
513431,113,3920,150,162,1,54,8,Māṇavā aññamaññaṃ oloketvā‘‘ kiṃ bhāsā nāmesā’’ ti vadiṃsu. 
513432,113,3920,163,166,1,28,3,Cittapaṇḍito maṅgalaṃ abhāsi. 
513433,113,3920,167,203,1,191,25,"Māṇavā bahi nikkhamitvā vaggavaggā hutvā tattha tattha nisīditvā bhāsaṃ sodhentā‘‘ caṇḍālabhāsā’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ are duṭṭhacaṇḍālā, ettakaṃ kālaṃ‘ brāhmaṇāmhā’ ti vatvā vañcayitthā’’ ti ubhopi te pothayiṃsu. "
513434,113,3920,204,231,1,125,18,"Atheko sappuriso‘‘ apethā’’ ti vāretvā‘‘ ayaṃ tumhākaṃ jātiyā doso, gacchatha katthaci deseva pabbajitvā jīvathā’’ ti te ubho uyyojesi. "
513435,113,3920,232,237,1,46,5,Māṇavā tesaṃ caṇḍālabhāvaṃ ācariyassa ārocesuṃ. 
513436,113,3921,2,16,1,119,14,Tepi araññaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā na cirasseva tato cavitvā nerañjarāya tīre migiyā kucchismiṃ nibbattiṃsu. 
513437,113,3921,17,28,1,84,10,"Te mātukucchito nikkhantakālato paṭṭhāya ekatova vicaranti, vinā bhavituṃ na sakkonti. "
513438,113,3921,29,54,1,189,23,"Te ekadivasaṃ gocaraṃ gahetvā ekasmiṃ rukkhamūle sīsena sīsaṃ, siṅgena siṅgaṃ, tuṇḍena tuṇḍaṃ allīyāpetvā romanthayamāne ṭhite disvā eko luddako sattiṃ khipitvā ekappahāreneva jīvitā voropesi. "
513439,113,3921,55,61,1,54,5,Tato cavitvā nammadānadītīre ukkusayoniyaṃ nibbattiṃsu. 
513440,113,3921,62,79,1,137,16,"Tatrāpi vuddhippatte gocaraṃ gahetvā sīsena sīsaṃ, tuṇḍena tuṇḍaṃ allīyāpetvā ṭhite disvā eko yaṭṭhiluddako ekappahāreneva bandhitvā vadhi. "
513441,113,3921,80,89,1,74,9,Tato pana cavitvā cittapaṇḍito kosambiyaṃ purohitassa putto hutvā nibbatti. 
513442,113,3921,90,95,1,55,5,Sambhūtapaṇḍito uttarapañcālarañño putto hutvā nibbatti. 
513443,113,3921,96,102,1,56,6,Te nāmaggahaṇadivasato paṭṭhāya attano jātiṃ anussariṃsu. 
513444,113,3921,103,116,1,127,12,"Tesu sambhūtapaṇḍito nirantaraṃ sarituṃ asakkonto catutthaṃ caṇḍālajātimeva anussarati, cittapaṇḍito paṭipāṭiyā catassopi jātiyo. "
513445,113,3921,117,130,1,130,12,So soḷasavassakāle nikkhamitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā jhānābhiññaṃ nibbattetvā jhānasukhena vītināmento vasi. 
513446,113,3921,131,145,1,136,13,Sambhūtapaṇḍitopi pitu accayena chattaṃ ussāpetvā chattamaṅgaladivaseyeva mahājanamajjhe maṅgalagītaṃ katvā udānavasena dve gāthā abhāsi. 
513447,113,3921,146,161,1,81,11,Taṃ sutvā‘‘ amhākaṃ rañño maṅgalagītan’’ ti orodhāpi gandhabbāpi tameva gītaṃ gāyanti. 
513448,113,3921,162,175,1,75,9,Anukkameneva‘‘ rañño piyagītan’’ ti sabbepi nagaravāsino manussā tameva gāyanti. 
513449,113,3922,2,59,1,400,47,"Cittapaṇḍitopi himavantapadese vasantoyeva‘‘ kiṃ nu kho mama bhātikena sambhūtena chattaṃ laddhaṃ, udāhu na vā’’ ti upadhārento laddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ navarajjaṃ tāva idāni gantvāpi bodhetuṃ na sakkhissāmi, mahallakakāle naṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ kathetvā pabbājessāmī’’ ti cintetvā paṇṇāsa vassāni agantvā rañño puttadhītāhi vaḍḍhitakāle iddhiyā gantvā uyyāne otaritvā maṅgalasilāpaṭṭe suvaṇṇapaṭimā viya nisīdi. "
513450,113,3922,60,69,1,58,9,Tasmiṃ khaṇe eko dārako taṃ gītaṃ gāyanto dārūni uddharati. 
