513455,113,3922,100,120,1,85,13,"‘‘ Bhante, aññānipi bahūni jānāmi, imāni pana dve rañño piyagītāni, tasmā imāneva gāyāmī’’ ti."
513456,113,3922,121,132,1,45,7,‘‘ Atthi pana rañño gītassa paṭigītaṃ gāyanto’’ ti?
513457,113,3922,133,140,1,16,3,‘‘ Natthi bhante’’ ti.
