513464,113,3925,2,14,1,63,9,"‘ ‘ Sabbaṃ narānaṃ saphalaṃ suciṇṇaṃ, na kammunā kiñcana moghamatthi; "
513465,113,3926,2,8,1,59,5,"Passāmi sambhūtaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ, sakammunā puññaphalūpapannaṃ. "
513466,113,3927,2,4,1,0,0,25.
513467,113,3928,2,14,1,63,9,"‘ ‘ Sabbaṃ narānaṃ saphalaṃ suciṇṇaṃ, na kammunā kiñcana moghamatthi; "
513468,113,3929,2,14,1,63,9,"Kaccinnu cittassapi evamevaṃ, iddho mano tassa yathāpi mayhan’’ ti. "
513469,113,3930,2,25,1,183,20,"Tattha na kammunā kiñcana {moghamatthī}ti sukatadukkaṭesu kammesu kiñcana ekakammampi moghaṃ nāma natthi, nipphalaṃ na hoti, vipākaṃ datvāva nassatīti aparāpariyavedanīyakammaṃ sandhāyāha. "
513470,113,3930,26,45,1,153,17,"Sambhūtan ti attānaṃ vadati, passāmahaṃ āyasmantaṃ sambhūtaṃ sakena kammena puññaphalūpapannaṃ, sakammaṃ nissāya puññaphalena upapannaṃ taṃ passāmīti attho. "
513471,113,3930,46,77,1,190,28,"Kaccinnu {cittassapī}ti mayañhi dvepi janā ekato hutvā na ciraṃ sīlaṃ rakkhimha, ahaṃ tāva tassa phalena mahantaṃ yasaṃ patto, kacci nu kho me bhātikassa cittassapi evameva mano iddho samiddhoti. "
