513478,113,3937,2,15,1,58,11,"‘ ‘ Bhavaṃ nu citto sutamaññato te, udāhu te koci naṃ etadakkhā; "
513479,113,3938,2,15,1,62,10,"Gāthā sugītā na mamatthi kaṅkhā, dadāmi te gāmavaraṃ satañcā’’ ti. "
513480,113,3939,2,19,1,109,15,Tattha sutamaññato {te}ti ahaṃ sambhūtassa bhātā citto nāmāti vadantassa cittasseva nu te santikā sutanti attho. 
