516690,113,5728,2,14,1,84,11,Kiṃ nu {socasī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ daharabhikkhuniṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
516691,113,5728,15,54,1,358,34,Sā kira sāvatthiyaṃ kuladhītā gharāvāse ādīnavaṃ disvā sāsane pabbajitvā ekadivasaṃ bhikkhunīhi saddhiṃ dhammasavanāya gantvā alaṅkatadhammāsane nisīditvā dhammaṃ desentassa dasabalassa aparimāṇapuññapabhāvābhinibbattaṃ uttamarūpasampattiyuttaṃ attabhāvaṃ oloketvā‘‘ pariciṇṇapubbā nu kho me bhavasmiṃ vicarantiyā imassa mahāpurisassa pādaparicārikā’’ ti cintesi. 
516692,113,5728,55,59,1,44,4,Athassā taṅkhaṇaññeva jātissarañāṇaṃ uppajji–
516693,113,5728,60,71,1,74,7,‘‘ chaddantavāraṇakāle ahaṃ imassa mahāpurisassa pādaparicārikā bhūtapubbā’’ ti. 
516694,113,5728,72,77,1,47,5,Athassā sarantiyā mahantaṃ pītipāmojjaṃ uppajji. 
516695,113,5728,78,84,1,46,6,Sā pītivegena mahāhasitaṃ hasitvā puna cintesi–
516696,113,5728,85,108,1,144,16,"‘‘ pādaparicārikā nāma sāmikānaṃ hitajjhāsayā appakā, ahitajjhāsayāva bahutarā, hitajjhāsayā nu kho ahaṃ imassa mahāpurisassa ahosiṃ, ahitajjhāsayā’’ ti. "
516697,113,5728,109,132,1,189,19,Sā anussaramānā‘‘ ahaṃ appamattakaṃ dosaṃ hadaye ṭhapetvā vīsaratanasatikaṃ chaddantamahāgajissaraṃ sonuttaraṃ nāma nesādaṃ pesetvā visapītasallena vijjhāpetvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpesin’’ ti addasa. 
516698,113,5728,133,148,1,108,13,"Athassā soko udapādi, hadayaṃ uṇhaṃ ahosi, sokaṃ sandhāretuṃ asakkontī assasitvā passasitvā mahāsaddena parodi. "
516699,113,5728,149,193,1,209,31,"Taṃ disvā satthā sitaṃ pātu karitvā‘‘ ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo sitassa pātukammāyā’’ ti bhikkhusaṅghena puṭṭho‘‘ bhikkhave, ayaṃ daharabhikkhunī pubbe mayi kataṃ aparādhaṃ saritvā rodatī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
516700,113,5729,2,12,1,102,9,Atīte himavantapadese chaddantadahaṃ upanissāya aṭṭhasahassā hatthināgā vasiṃsu iddhimantā vehāsaṅgamā. 
516701,113,5729,13,24,1,88,10,"Tadā bodhisatto jeṭṭhakavāraṇassa putto hutvā nibbatti, so sabbaseto ahosi rattamukhapādo. "
516702,113,5729,25,31,1,73,6,So aparabhāge vuddhippatto aṭṭhāsītihatthubbedho ahosi vīsaratanasatāyāmo. 
516703,113,5729,32,36,1,59,4,Aṭṭhapaṇṇāsahatthāya rajatadāmasadisāya soṇḍāya samannāgato. 
516704,113,5729,37,46,1,98,9,Dantā panassa parikkhepato pannarasahatthā ahesuṃ dīghato tiṃsahatthā chabbaṇṇaraṃsīhi samannāgatā. 
516705,113,5729,47,56,1,73,8,"So aṭṭhannaṃ nāgasahassānaṃ jeṭṭhako ahosi, pañcasate paccekabuddhe pūjesi. "
516706,113,5729,57,66,1,60,7,"Tassa dve aggamahesiyo ahesuṃ– cūḷasubhaddā, mahāsubhaddā cāti. "
516707,113,5729,67,71,1,55,4,Nāgarājā aṭṭhanāgasahassaparivāro kañcanaguhāyaṃ vasati. 
516708,113,5729,72,81,1,65,9,So pana chaddantadaho āyāmato ca vitthārato ca paṇṇāsayojano hoti. 
516709,113,5729,82,120,1,391,33,"Tassa majjhe dvādasayojanappamāṇe ṭhāne sevālo vā paṇakaṃ vā natthi, maṇikkhandhavaṇṇaudakameva santiṭṭhati, tadanantaraṃ yojanavitthataṃ suddhaṃ kallahāravanaṃ, taṃ udakaṃ parikkhipitvā ṭhitaṃ, tadanantaraṃ yojanavitthatameva suddhaṃ nīluppalavanaṃ taṃ parikkhipitvā ṭhitaṃ, tato yojanayojanavitthatāneva rattuppalasetuppalarattapadumasetapadumakumudavanāni purimaṃ purimaṃ parikkhipitvā ṭhitāni. "
516710,113,5729,121,135,1,141,14,Imesaṃ pana sattannaṃ vanānaṃ anantaraṃ sabbesampi tesaṃ kallahārādivanānaṃ vasena omissakavanaṃ yojanavitthatameva tāni parikkhipitvā ṭhitaṃ. 
516711,113,5729,136,154,1,230,16,"Tadanantaraṃ nāgānaṃ kaṭippamāṇe udake yojanavitthatameva rattasālivanaṃ, tadanantaraṃ udakapariyante yojanavitthatameva nīlapītalohitaodātasurabhisukhumakusumasamākiṇṇaṃ khuddakagacchavanaṃ, iti imāni dasa vanāni yojanavitthatāneva. "
516712,113,5729,155,200,1,366,31,"Tato khuddakarājamāsamahārājamāsamuggavanaṃ, tadanantaraṃ tipusaelālukalābukumbhaṇḍavallivanāni, tato pūgarukkhappamāṇaṃ ucchuvanaṃ, tato hatthidantappamāṇaphalaṃ kadalivanaṃ , tato sālavanaṃ, tadanantaraṃ cāṭippamāṇaphalaṃ panasavanaṃ, tato madhuraphalaṃ ciñcavanaṃ, tato ambavanaṃ, tato kapiṭṭhavanaṃ, tato omissako mahāvanasaṇḍo, tato veḷuvanaṃ, ayamassa tasmiṃ kāle sampatti. "
516713,113,5729,201,206,1,63,5,Saṃyuttaṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana idāni pavattamānasampattiyeva kathitā. 
516714,113,5730,2,8,1,48,6,Veḷuvanaṃ pana parikkhipitvā satta pabbatā ṭhitā. 
516715,113,5730,9,39,1,225,24,"Tesaṃ bāhirantato paṭṭhāya paṭhamo cūḷakāḷapabbato nāma, dutiyo mahākāḷapabbato nāma, tato udakapabbato nāma, tato candimapassapabbato nāma, tato sūriyapassapabbato nāma, tato maṇipassapabbato nāma, sattamo suvaṇṇapassapabbato nāma. "
516716,113,5730,40,49,1,86,9,So ubbedhato sattayojaniko chaddantadahaṃ parikkhipitvā pattassa mukhavaṭṭi viya ṭhito. 
516717,113,5730,50,62,1,110,11,"Tassa abbhantarimaṃ passaṃ suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ, tato nikkhantena obhāsena chaddantadaho samuggatabālasūriyo viya hoti. "
516718,113,5730,63,93,1,213,24,"Bāhirapabbatesu pana eko ubbedhato chayojaniko, eko pañca, eko cattāri, eko tīṇi, eko dve, eko yojaniko, evaṃ sattapabbataparikkhittassa pana tassa dahassa pubbuttarakaṇṇe udakavātappaharaṇokāse mahānigrodharukkho atthi. "
516719,113,5730,94,132,1,316,32,"Tassa khandho parikkhepato pañcayojaniko, ubbedhato sattayojaniko, catūsu disāsu catasso sākhā chayojanikā, uddhaṃ uggatasākhāpi chayojanikāva, iti so mūlato paṭṭhāya ubbedhena terasayojaniko, sākhānaṃ orimantato yāva pārimantā dvādasayojaniko, aṭṭhahi pārohasahassehi paṭimaṇḍito muṇḍamaṇipabbato viya vilāsamāno tiṭṭhati. "
516720,113,5730,133,140,1,96,7,Chaddantadahassa pana pacchimadisābhāge suvaṇṇapassapabbate dvādasayojanikā kañcanaguhā tiṭṭhati. 
516721,113,5730,141,149,1,89,8,Chaddanto nāma nāgarājā vassāratte hemante aṭṭhasahassanāgaparivuto kañcanaguhāyaṃ vasati. 
516722,113,5730,150,156,1,74,6,Gimhakāle udakavātaṃ sampaṭicchamāno mahānigrodhamūle pārohantare tiṭṭhatī. 
516723,113,5731,2,14,1,75,8,Athassa ekadivasaṃ‘‘ mahāsālavanaṃ pupphitan’’ ti taruṇanāgā āgantvā ārocayiṃsu. 
516724,113,5731,15,32,1,98,12,So saparivāro‘‘ sālakīḷaṃ kīḷissāmī’’ ti sālavanaṃ gantvā ekaṃ supupphitaṃ sālarukkhaṃ kumbhena pahari. 
516725,113,5731,33,46,1,120,12,"Tadā cūḷasubhaddā paṭivātapasse ṭhitā, tassā sarīre sukkhadaṇḍakamissakāni purāṇapaṇṇāni ceva tambakipillikāni ca patiṃsu. "
516726,113,5731,47,55,1,80,7,"Mahāsubhaddā adhovātapasse ṭhitā, tassā sarīre pupphareṇukiñjakkhapattāni patiṃsu. "
516727,113,5731,56,87,1,216,23,"Cūḷasubhaddā‘‘ ayaṃ nāgarājā attano piyabhariyāya upari pupphareṇukiñjakkhapattāni pātesi, mama sarīre sukkhadaṇḍakamissāni purāṇapaṇṇāni ceva tambakipillikāni ca pātesi, hotu, kātabbaṃ jānissāmī’’ ti mahāsatte veraṃ bandhi. "
516728,113,5732,2,9,1,69,7,Aparampi divasaṃ nāgarājā saparivāro nhānatthāya chaddantadahaṃ otari. 
516729,113,5732,10,21,1,82,10,Atha dve taruṇanāgā soṇḍāhi usirakalāpe gahetvā kelāsakūṭaṃ majjantā viya nhāpesuṃ. 
516730,113,5732,22,28,1,43,6,Tasmiṃ nhatvā uttiṇṇe dve kareṇuyo nhāpesuṃ. 
